snippet.title: Trailer Trashers Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Join with up to four players in this Hectic twin stick bullet bouncing frenzy. Challenge your friends in Death-match, Last Man Standing, Shotgun Soccer or crown yourself king of the couch in the all-including Party Mode!

Available NOW:
Nintendo eShop and Steam (pc, linux, mac)
Buy on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1248140/Trailer_Trashers/
On the Nintendo eShop
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/trailer-trashers-switch/
